## alsa
Key	XF86AudioMute			A	A	Exec exec amixer set Master toggle -q &
Key	XF86AudioRaiseVolume	A	A	Exec exec amixer -q sset Master 5%+ unmute
Key	XF86AudioLowerVolume	A	A	Exec exec amixer -q sset Master 5%- unmute

